"title": "1403: God, revelation of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1403: god, revelation of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God graciously makes himself known to humanity since people cannot discover him on their own. He achieves this in many ways, but supremely through his Son Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The necessity of revelation</h2>\n<h3>God is hidden from human view because of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:2\">ISA 59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:18\">DEU 31:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:15\">ISA 45:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:7\">ISA 64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:23\">EZK 39:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:4\">MIC 3:4</a></p>\n<h3>People are ignorant of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:23\">ACT 17:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:2\">EXO 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:10\">JDG 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:22\">JHN 4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:21\">JHN 15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:8\">GAL 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:5\">1TH 4:5</a></p>\n<h3>People cannot know God unaided</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25-Matt11:27\">MAT 11:25–11:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21-Luke10:22\">LUK 10:21–10:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:29\">JOB 34:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>The means by which God reveals himself</h2>\n<h3>In the Scriptures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:10\">PSA 19:7–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:19\">PSA 147:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:23\">PRO 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19-2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:19–1:21</a></p>\n<h3>By the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:26\">LUK 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:12\">LUK 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:10\">1CO 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12\">1CO 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:27\">1JN 2:27</a></p>\n<h3>Supremely in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:26\">JHN 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49\">JHN 12:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10\">JHN 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>In the creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">PSA 19:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26-Acts17:27\">ACT 17:26–17:27</a></p>\n<h3>Through the prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:7\">AMO 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:6\">NUM 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:17\">2SA 7:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:15\">1CH 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:27\">2SA 7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:25\">1CH 17:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:14\">ISA 22:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>In visions and dreams</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:17\">DAN 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:1\">ISA 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:24\">EZK 11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:1\">DAN 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:1\">NAM 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20\">MAT 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:12\">MAT 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:22\">MAT 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10\">ACT 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:9\">ACT 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:17-Acts22:18\">ACT 22:17–22:18</a></p>\n<h3>Face to face</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:8\">NUM 12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:30\">GEN 32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:9-Exod24:10\">EXO 24:9–24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:22\">JDG 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:5\">JOB 42:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>In the exodus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:5\">EXO 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:4\">EXO 14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:27\">1SA 2:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:5\">EZK 20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:9\">EZK 20:9</a></p>\n<h3>In special signs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:36-Judg6:40\">JDG 6:36–6:40</a> <em>Gideon's fleece</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:3-1Kgs13:5\">1KI 13:3–13:5</a> <em>an altar split apart</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:9-2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:9–20:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:7-Isa38:8\">ISA 38:7–38:8</a> <em>a shadow moving backwards</em></p>\n<h2>The nature of God's self-revelation in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>God reveals Jesus Christ's true identity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:17\">MAT 16:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:31\">JHN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15-Gal1:16\">GAL 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17-2Pet1:18\">2PE 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the visible image of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6\">PHP 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's glory is still to be fully revealed</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:30\">LUK 17:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:7\">1CO 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7\">2TH 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Things that God reveals</h2>\n<h3>Hidden mysteries</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:22\">DAN 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:16\">GEN 41:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:22\">JOB 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:28-Dan2:30\">DAN 2:28–2:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:47\">DAN 2:47</a></p>\n<h3>Future events</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:25\">GEN 41:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:15-1Sam9:16\">1SA 9:15–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:10\">2KI 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:18\">JER 11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:21\">JER 38:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:10\">ACT 18:9–18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:22-Acts27:24\">ACT 27:22–27:24</a></p>\n<h3>His righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21\">ROM 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:4\">REV 15:4</a></p>\n<h3>His wrath</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1\">NUM 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:7\">2SA 6:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:10\">1CH 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:11\">PSA 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>His salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:2\">PSA 98:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:10\">ISA 52:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:30-Luke2:32\">LUK 2:30–2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:6\">LUK 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11\">TIT 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>His glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:5\">ISA 40:5</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:10\">EXO 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:9\">EXO 33:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:5\">NUM 12:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:33\">DEU 1:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:12\">NEH 9:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:14\">PSA 78:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:39\">PSA 105:39</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:18-Exod33:23\">EXO 33:18–33:23</a> <em>the LORD shows his glory to Moses</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34\">EXO 40:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:2\">LEV 16:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:15\">DEU 31:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:4</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:24\">DEU 5:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:16\">PSA 102:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:2\">ISA 35:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:23\">ISA 44:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:2\">ISA 60:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55\">ACT 7:55</a></p>\n<h3>The mystery of the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:2-Eph3:3\">EPH 3:2–3:3</a></strong> <em>“mystery” in the NT means “something previously hidden, undiscoverable by human means but now revealed by God”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:11\">MAT 13:11</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:11\">MRK 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:10\">LUK 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25-Rom16:26\">ROM 16:25–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:23\">GAL 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:5-Eph3:6\">EPH 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:26-Col1:27\">COL 1:26–1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The revelation of God's will</h2>\n<h3>Physical means by which God reveals his will</h3>\n<p>By the Urim and Thummim:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:21\">NUM 27:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh18:6-Josh18:10\">JOS 18:6–18:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:7\">JON 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:26\">ACT 1:26</a></p>\n<h3>God's self-revelation makes his will plain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:11-Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:11–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:41\">JHN 9:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:7\">ROM 7:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's self-revelation is according to his own sovereign purpose</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:1\">ISA 65:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:30\">DAN 2:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:20\">ROM 10:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:11-Gal1:12\">GAL 1:11–1:12</a></p>",
